title: #92Noon! Fleck/Bercich/Siny/Cronin/JG
description: A border battle victory montage kicks off a Lovely Day, PJ Fleck calls in to celebrate the Gophers taking the Axe, Pete Bercich in studio, Sinykin laments his Packers, Courtney Cronin in studio final hour and JG finishes a busy Monday show!
